description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation Before Sleep: Let Go of the Day' from the channel Scott Ste Marie.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Scott Ste Marie is a Mindfulness Practitioner, Coach and Mentor. Through his lived experience with depression and anxiety he has seen what is truly possible in recovery, healing, and living authentically. If you feel at ease and comfortable with the videos on this channel and Scott's approach to emotional and mental well-being, the resources below may be helpful to you. 

SPEAK WITH SCOTT
https://www.scottstemarie.com/coaching...
